Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.06,OP Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real me... so hold me tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Bonjour! How are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about others today,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should be worrying more about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the result - no regrets, clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, you've all done your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, the new Lemon Angels will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best. I'll be watching from the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:10.46,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Talent Waiting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? I'm so nervous. My heart is beating so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi, when you're nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the best thing to do is to relax and focus on something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have to do my best. 'Cause even with all the training, I'm still not that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo, don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:42.20,Default Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three and fou-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Who's is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:04:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is yours, Miru-chan? I... I'm-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitoshi, time to go. Hitoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The rip...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just patched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go give it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audition will take place any moment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru-chan, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been mended.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, not by me though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was the one who ripped it after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Au... di... tion...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Self introduction. Make it appealing. They said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,it's gonna be a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not quite sure how to handle it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think if you just act natural, and sorta greet everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya know, "Hey, how's it goin'."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"How's it goin'?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not acting natural...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's time already? Miru-chan, hurry and change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:53.20,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I've made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya ya ya, welcome to the night of destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to see the start of a new legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon Angel, Act 2, The Last Audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember how they exploded onto the scene? Yeah! Lemon Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing off their success, today we have a real show for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:21.81,Default Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. It's just like being in the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Ten finalists! So, come on, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like the studio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look a little stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just have to leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri Hitoshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:08.57,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Áh! Katagiri Hitoshi? Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's time for the Self Intro appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entry number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Yohko Taguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet all of you. The reason I want to become a Lemon Angel is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ever since I was little, I've always admired idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought someday I wanted to be just like them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when I found out about the audition...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been going to singing school since way back. I'd like to thank my teacher from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think the reason I became a candidate was because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:08:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your days off, please fax me your drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my own blog, so please come and read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blog is called Asami's Miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next! Entry number five, Fuyumi Sakakibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to give it your all. Not just for you, but for Haruka too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-chan... yep, I gotta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it, but I'm from the Kansai region.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been going to a school for the performing arts since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An old friend of mine from there made me promise to do my best until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think it's okay, even for me, to try and see a dream through to it's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonjour! I'm Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:09:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the country I was born in, bonjour means good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though saying good morning at night? The world of show business has weird customs, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, hello, everyone. Actually, I'm not used to being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yayoi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done photo spreads!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't call me Yayoi! I'm Saya! Yuki Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! A string of cool comments. Gives me the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And next we have entry number 11, Tomo Minaguchi.  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo-chan's walking is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Tomo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously? No one knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with this many people here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hold on! It was in the magazine. At least one of you should have checked it out beforehand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all teasing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.20,Default Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Minaguchi Tomo, now remember that next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't even begin to cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now the last one. Entry number twelve, Miru Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Miru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, shall we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's hear your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Miru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who selected her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people are very reserved, though not many take it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can do the whole "pretty as a picture" thing fairly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, appeal time is over. We'll continue in 30 minutes. See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lacked something! This is not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was nothing, the real challenge is just starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miru. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking so depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing my temper, and picking a fight. Hey, Saya, tell me the secret to stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Saya, you're used to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for me,if I mess up the next part, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.28,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Judge Waiting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it, Hitoshi? See anyone you think fits the bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I slept through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:13:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwa Miki. Wear fewer neckties. That rag will just kill your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead wear things with elastic collars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:23.24,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this. I'll never reach Ann...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:26.82,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so sad. Both her parents are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:30.20,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, could we speak with the survivor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:34.16,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,They say she hasn't said a word. Recovery will be very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:39.25,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,You're babying her. It's been long enough, time to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.84,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we should have her go outside for a little bit, even if it doesn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.88,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.42,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you come out, Miru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:48.34,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru-chan, your aunt and uncle are worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.39,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.47,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.89,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa-san
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.43,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good morning. We will now begin our broadcasting day. Capitol TTTV TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:00.94,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing we of the Lemon Angels can do is send out our songs to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:05.78,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think that's actually a way to make us more alive to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:10.41,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy if I could bring some encouragement to everyone, even if it's just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:14.58,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,The song we recorded this week will be a good representation of us. I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:20.13,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,For those out there who wish to grow, and find a way to become a new person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:24.42,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon Angel... Ann...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru-chan, why are you back here all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you worrying about the same thing I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about not having done so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the same thing. You managed to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine, since you sing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, oh, yeah. Want to listen together? It'll cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.01,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's time for the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the winners are:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saya Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erika Campbell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuyumi Sakakibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?, Huh?, What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Miru Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru-chan, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And lastly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final Angel is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo Minaguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Tomo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now don't slow us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the leader, Miki Suwa! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time that we all clapped our hands. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations. Here we now have the new Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go forth and surpass the legend, my six lovely stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It still doesn't feel real. We're really Lemon Angels, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? We're only finally at the starting line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dream is still ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This is where it starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to congratulate everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? Keiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sukina Keiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I've been asked to be the manager for Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogure-san asked me if I would come on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I hope we work well together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! With Keiko here, there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go overboard Yayoi-cha... I mean Saya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Okay, everyone, let's take over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Busy day. Though it's just the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.15,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Yui-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:21:00.82,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! It's a miracle! God must've made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.20,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:07.99,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to sing your songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who this could be? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while. I wonder if you remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Next Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Actually I was asked by Himuro-san to please have you come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, no way! Don't tell me, it's something special for having passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, well we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do come, you'll definitely see something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himuro-san did that for me? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll probably enjoy it. Much more than joining the Lemon Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:07.80,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the first day i laid eyes on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:07.80,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,hajimete negatta hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:16.14,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason my heart can't seem to rest
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:16.14,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,nazeka kokoro ga nemuren nakunatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:24.90,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the courage to pick up the phone and call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:24.90,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,denwa wa suru yuuki mo nai kawari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:35.19,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, if for only a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:35.19,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,toomawari guuzen wo kiri
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:39.71,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,When girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:39.71,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,onna no ko tachi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:43.80,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,are in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:43.80,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,koi wo suru ta bi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:49.76,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,...They become lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:49.76,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,sabishigari ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:52.85,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,As they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:52.85,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,itsudaatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:55.00,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:55.00,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:23:10.01,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,because when in love, this feeling says no one else but you will do 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:23:10.01,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,nee kono kimochi kimi igai wa arienai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:12.07,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:12.07,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls in love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:18.62,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me closer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:18.62,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Motto dakishimete yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.13,0:23:28.76,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,and take me to a world I can only dream about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.13,0:23:28.76,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Yume no naka made tsuretette
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:33.51,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(268,69)}Next Time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've really become Lemon Angels!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you so nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh? But, Saya, aren't you wondering who'll become the main vocal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it's about that, it'll be me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.78,0:23:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Lemon Angel Project, episode 7, "I want to know you."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Kogure-san thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:23:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares what he thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.99,0:23:59.96,PreviewTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(634,444)}I want to know you